# {{†}} to [[comprehend]]; to [[realise]]; to [[understand]]
# {{lb|zh|transitive}} to [[learn]]; to [[study]]
#: {{zh-x|學習|to study; to learn}}
#: {{zh-x|我 打算 學 攝影。|I plan to '''learn''' photography.}}
#* {{zh-x|我 父母親 希望 我 學 醫，但是 我 不 願意。|My parents hoped I would '''study''' medicine, but I didn't want to.}}
# {{lb|zh|transitive}} to [[learn]] to do something (to get into the habit)
#* {{zh-x|老師 叫 極 佢 都 唔 肯 學 講 唔該。|He refuses to '''learn''' to say thank you, even if his teacher asked him many times.|C}}
#* {{zh-x|佢 學 慣 咗 玩 呢{ni1} 種 遊戲。|He '''got used''' to play this game.|C}}
#* {{zh-x|佢 學 咗 講 美國 口音，但係 去 到 英國 嘅 時候，佢 學 講 英國 口音，返去 美國 之後，佢 學 返 講 美國 口音。|He '''learned''' to speak with an American accent, but when he was in United Kingdom, he '''learned''' to speak with a British accent, and when he came back to United States, he re'''learned''' to speak with an American accent.|C}}
# to [[imitate]]; to [[copy]]; to [[mimic]]
#: {{zh-x|鸚鵡 學 人 語。|Parrots '''imitate''' human speech.}}
#* {{zh-x|我 妹妹 什麼 都 學 我。|My little sister likes to '''copy''' everything I do.}}
#* {{zh-x|學 人哋 用 叉 食飯|'''imitate''' others and use a fork to eat|C}}
